formula:
\begin{array}{lcr}
BaseDamageModifier & = & \lfloor BaseMaxDamage + ChaosGauntlets + Charge\rfloor\\
\\
PrimaryMagicDamage & = & \lfloor BaseDamageModifier * (1 + min(1,(VisibleBonuses - Void) * ShadowBonus) + Void + Salve + Avarice + SmokeBattlestaff + VirtusRobesAncientBonus + Prayer)\rfloor\\
\\
PreHitRoll & = & \Bigg\lfloor\bigg\lfloor\Big\lfloor\lfloor PrimaryMagicDamage * (1 + Slayer)\rfloor * (1 + SceptreWilderness)\Big\rfloor * (1 + AccursedSceptreSpecialAttack)\bigg\rfloor * (1 + Tomes)\Bigg\rfloor\\
\\
HitRoll & = & \lfloor max(1,random(0,PreHitRoll))\rfloor\\
\\
PostHitRoll & = & \bigg\lfloor\Big\lfloor\lfloor HitRoll * (1 + MarkOfDarkness)\rfloor * (1 + AhrimsDamned)\Big\rfloor * (1 + CastleWarsBraclet)\bigg\rfloor\\
\end{array}

\begin{array}{lcr}

\\
PreHitRoll & = & \Bigg\lfloor\bigg\lfloor\Big\lfloor\lfloor PrimaryMagicDamage * (1 + Slayer)\rfloor * (1 + SceptreWilderness)\Big\rfloor * (1 + AccursedSceptreSpecialAttack)\bigg\rfloor * (1 + Tomes)\Bigg\rfloor\\

HitRoll & = & \lfloor max(1,random(0,PreHitRoll))\rfloor\\

\end{array}

formula:
\begin{align}
Base &= \frac{1}{4} \times (Defence + Hitpoints + \lfloor \frac{1}{2} \times Prayer \rfloor) \\
Melee &= \frac{13}{40} \times (Attack + Strength) \\
Range &= \frac{13}{40} \times \lfloor \frac{3}{2} \times Ranged \rfloor \\
Mage &= \frac{13}{40} \times \lfloor \frac{3}{2} \times Magic \rfloor \\
Final &= \lfloor Base + max(Melee, Range, Mage) \rfloor
\end{align}
raw:
\begin{align}
Base &= \frac{1}{4} \times (Defence + Hitpoints + \lfloor \frac{1}{2} \times Prayer \rfloor) \\
Melee &= \frac{13}{40} \times (Attack + Strength) \\
Range &= \frac{13}{40} \times \lfloor \frac{3}{2} \times Ranged \rfloor \\
Mage &= \frac{13}{40} \times \lfloor \frac{3}{2} \times Magic \rfloor \\
Final &= \lfloor Base + max(Melee, Range, Mage) \rfloor
\end{align}
